> systems I have installed I notice similar timeout problems when the ISA scsi
> card was sharing an IRQ with another device, you sound card (if any) may be
Sharing interrupts with another ISA device is not a legal configuration
for most device pairs. In fact unless you went and drilled holes in the cards
and stuff you should assume its definitely not valid
